{"type": "article", "id": 61187, "title": "这一系列门牌号设计，带你领略复古风潮｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-02-13T23:35:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 45607, "name": "GRT Architects"}, {"id": 56622, "name": "KAZA Concrete"}, {"id": 27093, "name": "Petite Friture"}, {"id": 11593, "name": "Yoox"}, {"id": 56623, "name": "Rob Pruitt"}, {"id": 31050, "name": "Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte"}, {"id": 7901, "name": "NakNak"}, {"id": 47123, "name": "Noé Duchaufour Lawrance"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 138, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190213210129gKWeSLUnqb6jAJsB.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #484848; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #484848} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>WIRE ALPHABET by NakNak</h3><p>行走在欧洲街头时常被造型各异的特色门牌所吸引，它是每个家庭的个性注解，也构成了人对家的第一印象。</p><p>早年曾留学瑞典的 NakNak 品牌设计总监曾彦文一直对门牌号的设计十分着迷。于是在 NakNak 品牌成立初便确定了要开发一系列复古门牌号的计划。当每一个空间都有独特标志时，整个建筑甚至城市都活泼有趣起来。</p><p>在细心研究了众多设计师后，曾彦文力邀品牌的视觉顾问韩国设计师 Kyuhyung Cho 来担任复古门牌号的设计。 Kyuhyung Cho 擅长以图解方式，设计平面艺术品和家具产品，尤其喜爱研究北欧和东亚设计。而曾担任瑞典著名时尚品牌 Acne 艺术指导的瑞典设计师 Erik Olovsson 更是对这个设计项目非常感兴趣，随后便一同加入到整个设计中来。</p><p>他们将平面化的数字进行多层立体化设计，以饱满的造型，重塑门牌的复古风潮，同时融入时下流行的可爱俏皮元素，让复古门牌成为街头潮文化的全新注解。更令人意想不到的是，产品上线不久后，英国的一家知名字体设计公司便联络上了设计师们，希望能把整套设计开发成电脑字体。</p><p>售价 299 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.3-c-s.w4002-21056647372.9.752850ad6WbRNI&amp;id=581769959041\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210214WDudqnSr6oxgCEYZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708920\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210214xIRt10OXK8eTYFJ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708920\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210214XmKx9iYThEeFVJ1c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708920\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210215aOw0vcrChTb8sPUL.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210232GdJSZPih0oK4TQW6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210232MdNDwKXOAoIUJHTu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210232HGgj1Mlt34me60Fc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.506000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210232Y53UHlbw6PzyVmqk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Legs by  Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte </h3><p>Legs 是当代家居中独一无二的家具的集合；它们皆由不对称的粉末涂层钢结构构成，出自 Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte  之手。</p><p>这些家具冷硬的钢结构与其弯曲的铰接和平坦且连续的表面形成了鲜明的对比。每件家具都呈现出不同的比例尺度。有些家具更加适合在慵懒的周末的清晨使用，让你能够享受一个放纵的早晨；有些家具在你离开家门时会使用到；还有些家具则可供人们在晚上使用，放松身心，恢复元气。无论它们的特点如何，你都会庆幸这些家具的奇异感和陌生感：它们原本仅仅存在于幻想之中，而现在，它们来到了现实中，扎根于你家的地板之上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210341fQ9qpJRO0UrvynaD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210342ZHv21Bc6I0QCdKX5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210341aLpiFg5vnlTQ7Orx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210342mXtHKoJUMlcWuvLk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210342xjXk1i9HTRIZyDAh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210342uHKX8oRQwYSlB5zI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210343eKWkdOaACZyiXcYs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210343BbiQI9jhXqHEfMAG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.pevdp.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Migration Moving Blankets by Rob Pruitt for Yoox</h3><p>美国艺术家 Rob Pruitt 推出了一系列用于移动家具的被子，名为 Migration Moving Blankets 。这一系列是专为线上零售商 Yoox 设计的，并在 2019 年 Nomad 设计展上首次亮相， Rob Pruitt 为此设计了 40 款独特的限量版被子，目的是把家具完好无损地包裹起来，以便在移动时保护它们免受破损或者磕碰。</p><p>“在自然界中，所有类型的物种都会季节性地迁移以寻找安全和舒适感，同时，人类也会迁移以逃避暴政和专制，或更简单地重新安置以寻求更好的生活，”Pruitt 解释道。</p><p>他收集了旧的移动毯子，这些毯子通常由工业纺织品的碎片缝合在一起，并将这些工厂制作的毯子覆盖在他做的像素化丝网印刷品上。虽然这些设计参考了数字像素化，但也参考了纺织品制造商用来制造拼布织物的传统绗缝方块。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902132104279ncp8OtLXlhN1gGQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.273266\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210427xRTVmABkYPlN5fqn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210428pQYIEo4TWi8qRLNs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.273266\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210427evu4SiREJ7W1Lylh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/02/12/rob-pruitt-migration-moving-blanket-nomad-design-fair/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Méditerranéa Lighting Collection by Petite Friture</h3><p>在今年的科隆国际家具展上，法国设计品牌 Petite Friture 为其受欢迎的 Méditerranéa 系列再添新款，仍旧是出自法国设计师 Noé Duchaufour Lawrance 之手。</p><p>垂褶灯具的灵感来自于在地中海阳台微风中漂浮的轻盈衣物的场景。它们的金属“布”垂落而下，并通过几何穿孔散射光线，在周围的表面上形成美丽的图案。</p><p>该系列最初采用拉丝黄铜制成，也可换成黑色和白色饰面。Méditerranéa 系列有阅读灯、落地灯、壁灯和吊灯。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210515jc0AQ4iraRlNyKs2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210515jdNVcZzwACBx7D5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902132105157J23PywvjdEh8qVT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902132105155bfKMHh3GjJ6B94v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210515fDZPM7uIOCSsea9N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210515eT63QsNjHEYLZU5W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210516piEU4FTwLm07O3MD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210516WzOF9XNdVMoAvyc8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210516rwTjQHvdObcU2olF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748437\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210516qRkdLBhZT54GxaX9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://petitefriture.com/en/108-mediterranea\" rel=\"nofollow\">Petite Friture</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Flutes and Reeds Collection by GRT Architects for KAZA Concrete</h3><p>水泥墙砖品牌 KAZA Concrete 推出了最新系列瓷砖 Flutes and Reeds，出自 GRT Architects 团队之手。</p><p>整个系列采用了一些建筑最古老的表面装饰，对其进行了现代版的诠释。比如希腊建筑中常见的柱子、壁柱和墙壁上的凹槽。Flutes and Reeds 系列包括四种瓷砖设计：Single Flute，Triple Flute,，Single Reed 和 Double Reed。</p><p>每个瓷砖“切片”是标准凹槽或柱体的一部分，并提供一系列网格排列选项。但是当以标准方式排列时，它们形成类似于具有微妙几何变化的经典版本样式。但旋转瓷砖，又会突然创造一个新的模式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210559nvrgWjhaAVtDL30u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.475309\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210559wdCTH9IhAjuamZnx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210600oiCFBHPq1XWJVzOc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745679\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902132106001GCl7LgI9qVQZdOU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667901\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213210600NecqhukavUP6LMFB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672840\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902132106013BS0lgTWkY8HDGq2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.683951\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-tile-collection-that-takes-on-architectures-oldest-embellishments/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}